  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What kind of game is it?</h2><br>A turn-based roguelike RPG that's easy to pick up and play!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How is it played?</h2><br>All you need to do is move up, down, left, and right! No inventory management or additional actions required!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050800/extras/12c96629aff4075cd63459e8a08f8c56.webp?t=1726365575\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050800/extras/12c96629aff4075cd63459e8a08f8c56.poster.avif?t=1726365575\" class=\"bb_img\" width=230 height=230 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How difficult is the game?</h2><br>Casual yet challenging! Strategic depth is preserved!<br><br>The difficulty is adjusted to provide a satisfying challenge even for seasoned roguelike players!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How much content is there?</h2><br>In addition to roguelike stages, there are over 20 diverse stages, including puzzles, tower defense, survival, and mystery-solving!",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What kind of game is it?</h2><br>A turn-based roguelike RPG that's easy to pick up and play!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How is it played?</h2><br>All you need to do is move up, down, left, and right! No inventory management or additional actions required!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050800/extras/12c96629aff4075cd63459e8a08f8c56.webp?t=1726365575\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050800/extras/12c96629aff4075cd63459e8a08f8c56.poster.avif?t=1726365575\" class=\"bb_img\" width=230 height=230 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How difficult is the game?</h2><br>Casual yet challenging! Strategic depth is preserved!<br><br>The difficulty is adjusted to provide a satisfying challenge even for seasoned roguelike players!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How much content is there?</h2><br>In addition to roguelike stages, there are over 20 diverse stages, including puzzles, tower defense, survival, and mystery-solving!",
